<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>تم التسجيل - Paintello Pro</title>

  <!-- Bootstrap & Font Awesome -->
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <!-- Meta Pixel Base Code (only if not already loaded) -->
  <% if (typeof fbPixelId !== 'undefined') { %>
  <script>
    !function(f,b,e,v,n,t,s)
    {if(f.fbq)return;n=f.fbq=function(){n.callMethod?
    n.callMethod.apply(n,arguments):n.queue.push(arguments)};
    if(!f._fbq)f._fbq=n;n.push=n;n.loaded=!0;n.version='2.0';
    n.queue=[];t=b.createElement(e);t.async=!0;
    t.src=v;s=b.getElementsByTagName(e)[0];
    s.parentNode.insertBefore(t,s)}(window, document,'script',
    'https://connect.facebook.net/en_US/fbevents.js');
    fbq('init', '<%= fbPixelId %>');
  </script>
  <% } %>

  <style>
    :root {
      --primary-blue: #295797;
      --accent-blue: #1C84C1;
      --primary-dark: #1E3F5C;
      --bg-light: #E8EEF6;
      --bg-white: #FFFFFF;
      --border-light: #D1DCE6;
      --shadow-sm: 0 2px 8px rgba(41,87,151,0.08);
      --shadow-md: 0 4px 12px rgba(41,87,151,0.12);
      --text-dark: #2D3748;
      --text-gray: #4A5568;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', 'Tajawal', sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg-light);
      margin: 0;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      direction: rtl;
    }

    .pending-container {
      max-width: 550px;
      width: 90%;
      margin: 20px;
    }

    .pending-card {
      background: var(--bg-white);
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 40px 30px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
      border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
      text-align: center;
    }

    .pending-icon {
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
      background: #d4edda;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin: 0 auto 24px;
      font-size: 36px;
      color: #28a745;
    }

    .pending-card h1 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--primary-blue);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .pending-card p {
      color: var(--text-gray);
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--primary-blue);
      color: white;
      border: none;
      padding: 12px 32px;
      border-radius: 40px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: var(--primary-dark);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
      color: white;
    }

    .redirect-note {
      color: var(--text-gray);
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .seconds-counter {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: var(--accent-blue);
    }

    @media (max-width: 576px) {
      .pending-card {
        padding: 30px 20px;
      }
      .pending-card h1 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="pending-container">
    <div class="pending-card">
      <div class="pending-icon">
        <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
      </div>
      <h1>تم التسجيل بنجاح!</h1>
      <p>
        حسابك قيد المراجعة حاليًا. سيتم تفعيل حسابك بعد التحقق من المعلومات التي قدمتها.<br>
        سنقوم بإعلامك فور الانتهاء من المراجعة.
      </p>
      
      <a href="<%= loginUrl %>" class="btn-primary">
        <i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt"></i> الذهاب إلى تسجيل الدخول
      </a>
      
      <p class="redirect-note">
        سيتم توجيهك تلقائيًا إلى صفحة الدخول خلال <span class="seconds-counter" id="countdown">5</span> ثوانٍ
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- CompleteRegistration Pixel (browser side) -->
  <script>
    (function() {
      // Fire the browser CompleteRegistration pixel with the same event ID
      if (typeof fbq !== 'undefined') {
        fbq('track', 'CompleteRegistration', {}, {
          eventID: '<%= completeRegistrationId %>'
        });
        console.log('🎯 Browser CompleteRegistration sent with ID:', '<%= completeRegistrationId %>');
      } else {
        console.warn('Meta Pixel not loaded – browser event not sent');
      }

      // Auto-redirect countdown
      var secondsLeft = 5;
      var countdownEl = document.getElementById('countdown');
      var loginUrl = '<%= loginUrl %>';

      var timer = setInterval(function() {
        secondsLeft--;
        if (countdownEl) countdownEl.textContent = secondsLeft;
        if (secondsLeft <= 0) {
          clearInterval(timer);
          window.location.href = loginUrl;
        }
      }, 1000);
    })();
  </script>
</body>
</html>
